<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EverettBlayne Accounting | Home</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Colors: 
           Dark Grey/Plum: #51484f
           Deep Maroon: #7a203e
           Bright Maroon: #96254a
           Muted Mauve/Grey: #8b8589 
        */

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #fbfbfb;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
        
        /* Navigation / Header */
        header {
            background: #51484f; /* Dark Grey/Plum */
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 4rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 6px solid #7a203e; /* Deep Maroon accent */
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            color: #e2e0e1;
        }
        
        /* Buttons */
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #7a203e; /* Deep Maroon */
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #96254a; /* Bright Maroon on hover */
        }

        /* Services Hub Section */
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            color: #51484f;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .services-grid {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        
        /* Service Cards */
        .service-card {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
            max-width: 350px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-top: 5px solid #8b8589; /* Muted Mauve accent */
            padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none; /* Removes underline from links */
            color: inherit; /* Keeps text color normal even though it's a link */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            border-top-color: #96254a; /* Brightens on hover */
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .service-card h3 {
            color: #51484f;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        
        .service-card p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .card-link-text {
            color: #7a203e;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            background: #8b8589; /* Muted Mauve */
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>EverettBlayne Accounting</h1>
            <p>Providing precision bookkeeping, tax strategy, and financial consulting to help your business operate efficiently and scale confidently.</p>
            <a href="#services" class="cta-button">Explore Our Services</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container" id="services" style="margin-top: 4rem;">
        <h2 class="section-title">How Can We Help Your Business?</h2>
        
        <div class="services-grid">
            
            <a href="bookkeeping.html" class="service-card">
                <h3>Bookkeeping</h3>
                <p>From essential monthly compliance and reconciliations to dedicated operational support and custom workflow automation.</p>
                <span class="card-link-text">View Pricing & Plans &rarr;</span>
            </a>

            <a href="taxes.html" class="service-card">
                <h3>Tax Services</h3>
                <p>Strategic tax planning and preparation designed to minimize liability and keep you compliant with all current regulations.</p>
                <span class="card-link-text">Learn More &rarr;</span>
            </a>

            <a href="consultations.html" class="service-card">
                <h3>Consultations</h3>
                <p>Deep-dive advisory sessions focusing on cost accounting, job order setups, and database workflow efficiency.</p>
                <span class="card-link-text">Book a Session &rarr;</span>
            </a>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 EverettBlayne Accounting. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
